<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .status {
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .status-verified {
      background-color: #d4edda;
      color: #155724;
    }
    .status-rejected {
      background-color: #f8d7da;
      color: #721c24;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #FEDC00;
      color: #010101;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 40px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Document Verification Status</h1>
    </div>

    <p>Dear {{name}},</p>

    <p>Your document "{{documentName}}" has been reviewed.</p>

    <div class="status {{#if isVerified}}status-verified{{else}}status-rejected{{/if}}">
      <h2>Status: {{status}}</h2>
      {{#if message}}
        <p>{{message}}</p>
      {{/if}}
    </div>

    {{#unless isVerified}}
      <div>
        <h3>Next Steps:</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Review the feedback provided</li>
          <li>Make necessary corrections</li>
          <li>Upload the updated document</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    {{/unless}}

    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="{{portalUrl}}" class="button">View Details</a>
    </p>

    <p>If you have any questions, please contact us:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Email: support@zoomcreatives.jp</li>
      <li>Phone: 03-6764-5723</li>
      <li>Mobile: 090-6494-5723</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>© {{year}} Zoom Creatives. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>
        〒130-0012 東京都墨田区太平1-11-7 グランドステータスKIYA2F<br>
        Tokyo-To, Sumida-Ku, Taihei 1-11-7 Grand Status KIYA 2F, 130-0012
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>